Title

Handling Missing Values

Content

Introduction

Missing values can affect the accuracy of analysis and visualizations. Therefore, the dataset was examined before building dashboards.

Observations

Columns such as ca, thal, and oldpeak contained some missing values.
Numerical missing values were ignored where appropriate or handled during analysis.
Tableau automatically excluded null values from affected charts.
Records with sufficient information were used for visualization.

Outcome

The remaining data was sufficient to generate accurate dashboards and insights.

